docs.name: NGHTHYP - Night Floor
docs.description:
From album "HYVE Vol. 1", 2021. Pretty fun and ravey hard dance album, give it a listen. I'm pretty sure I'll map at least one other track from this one.

Swing eBPM: 320.00 (Flicks, lots of flicks)
NJS: 19.5

Techy map with a gimmick or two, 320bpm flicks, funny 1/6 timings, one (1) vision block, wall spam and some dance walls. It's accable though. I think it's fun but I've come to understand that I like 🗑️ when it comes to maps.

Reup #1: Fixed vision blocking walls.

Lights mostly with lolighter.

Where to report that the streams (or maybe 0-end) suck: riisi#9847
